data.description: Beautiful home in the mountains just minutes from the Blue Ridge Parkway on 24 acres. This land is full of wildlife and comes with a pond in a private setting. Property features a 2 car carport and 2 car detached garage by the house, and down the hill another 4 bay garage with pit and lift.  This property also boasts 2 paved driveways and a beautiful covered front porch perfect for dreaming your day away.  Close to Phillpot Lake, Fairystone Park and the Town of Floyd, This retreat is a beautiful playground for kayaking, boating, fishing, hunting and hiking. Book your tour now so you can spend the Holidays in this beautiful home!
